    },
    {
      "segment_id": "3daf1b88",
      "source_content": "### Basic",
      "source_content_hash": "40d6e857abf13beb94484f2bcc31ef42239e57b236f03e57852e7039bd689134",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### 基本"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "f6168993",
      "source_content": "A basic `Card` component expects at least a heading, used as a title.",
      "source_content_hash": "56b5bdfadd105a45c6da8357608f9436a048bc1a3dc77d50a004c3f75fa5ce4f",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "基本的な `Card` コンポーネントには、少なくともタイトルとして使用する見出しが必要です。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "cbbebf8e",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card>\n  <Card.Heading>Filter by name</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Description>Filter data by query.</Card.Description>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "22f7df4a9015b64812180fa487b8223915b17a6fcd880308ea157b3f6eb858d6",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_cbbebf8e"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "3c36424c",
      "source_content": "### Multiple metadata elements",
      "source_content_hash": "8ea9a29a56f22a234df659a1cf170363e9490c3dd991ea13d4f20ee60dc82708",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### 複数のメタデータ要素"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "26524352",
      "source_content": "For providing metadata elements, which can be any extra information for the card, `Card.Meta` component should be used. If metadata consists of multiple strings, each of them has to be escaped (wrapped in brackets `{}`) or better passed in as an array.",
      "source_content_hash": "8c470687838133317d2d4add2edee00d8daf1e44aa73f736b7506de2afa65cc5",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "メタデータ要素（カードの追加情報）を提供するには、`Card.Meta` コンポーネントを使用する必要があります。メタデータが複数の文字列で構成されている場合、それぞれを中括弧 `{}` で囲むか、配列として渡すことが推奨されます。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "b017063d",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card>\n  <Card.Heading>Test dashboard</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Meta>{['Folder: Test', 'Views: 100']}</Card.Meta>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "b599f1d7c601c07c34455e5684ce922a918941657a61a2c1d65f89b058672800",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_b017063d"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "c3a738de",
      "source_content": "Metadata also accepts HTML elements, which could be links, for example. For elements that are not strings, a `key` prop has to be manually specified.",
      "source_content_hash": "ac626932f345377a4b7b36596e986f8cefec283132b4404f29d056420a2997d5",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "メタデータはHTML要素（例えばリンク）も受け入れます。文字列以外の要素の場合、`key` プロパティを手動で指定する必要があります。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "bca33820",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card>\n  <Card.Heading>Test dashboard</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Meta>\n    Grafana\n    <a key=\"prom-link\" href=\"https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\">\n      https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\n    </a>\n  </Card.Meta>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "d5d2c2ac368cfed3df5086bf6c44a1623ee2f0f8288ab97cc088fcacb32bd1f5",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_bca33820"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "98d26038",
      "source_content": "The separator for multiple metadata elements defaults to a vertical line `|`, but can be customised.",
      "source_content_hash": "08572dd160ac9c7e8f51f62df175951b379a344415560421871e59f8044d09a7",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "複数のメタデータ要素の区切り文字はデフォルトで縦棒 `|` ですが、カスタマイズ可能です。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "f275f5fd",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card>\n  <Card.Heading>Test dashboard</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Meta separator={'-'}>\n    Grafana\n    <a key=\"prom-link\" href=\"https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\">\n      https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\n    </a>\n  </Card.Meta>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "931e8be92b7ea53607bfc6f6559b2b7f9869900b90a2cd7875e798ffd97c4ccf",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_f275f5fd"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a5a4323e",
      "source_content": "### Tags",
      "source_content_hash": "6518afe373ff19591fc1a0f2e11a79e2334cf2eddb46df3750e459ec227cd20f",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### タグ"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "657c2b20",
      "source_content": "Tags can be rendered inside the Card, by being wrapped in `Card.Tags` component. Note that this component does not provide any tag styling and that should be handled by the children. It is recommended to use it with Grafana-UI's `TagList` component.",
      "source_content_hash": "2b7a7194fba5f56dbbdeb737163436cbf79b5e350384a400fe56863be335a0a5",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "タグは `Card.Tags` コンポーネント内にラップすることでカード内に表示できます。このコンポーネント自体はタグのスタイリングを提供しないため、子要素で処理する必要があります。Grafana-UIの `TagList` コンポーネントとの併用が推奨されます。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "52388877",
      "source_content": "### As a link",
      "source_content_hash": "15b147eaf14cf8e50ba23e8a19e9535ee846c578d5245e63fe6c735594a37076",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### リンクとして使用"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "eab056be",
      "source_content": "Card can be used as a clickable link item by specifying `href` prop.",
      "source_content_hash": "a8e09ed7cdb1510870a302720f6b451bdd36b250972a4d29594ef9dacaffc0d7",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "`href` プロパティを指定することで、カードをクリック可能なリンクアイテムとして使用できます。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "9f3b4022",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card href=\"https://grafana.com\">\n  <Card.Heading>Redirect to Grafana</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Description>Clicking this card will redirect to grafana website</Card.Description>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "84fbde794c13c992a91ef9c2dbfe7b9ef1f73ac5294e22ccf690457411800388",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_9f3b4022"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "8a9b6c26",
      "source_content": "### As a button",
      "source_content_hash": "2a350926dcaeeefed818cfde0d7a9ff3815d886d7c4390c3d4c9bca3ad01cb4d",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### ボタンとして使用"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "a1fa5396",
      "source_content": "Card can be used as a clickable button item by specifying `onClick` prop.",
      "source_content_hash": "e00b5369cd1073f8b9925b0bd592f7647e5b884882155adaa773799ad6bcd05b",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "`onClick` プロパティを指定することで、カードをクリック可能なボタンアイテムとして使用できます。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "8c3563d3",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card onClick={() => alert('Hello, Grafana!')}>\n  <Card.Heading>Hello, Grafana</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Description>Clicking this card will create an alert</Card.Description>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "d15d73c9e93da1c6b41ac82a5bf952c6509734b0ad8cbb04426ffccc13a6fa5e",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_8c3563d3"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "39db08de",
      "source_content": "#### Note",
      "source_content_hash": "ad8edba4c7789591022c73a8bd55a616580fb364fb3e18eaad9e0a59a894ac04",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "#### 注意"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "785750ac",
      "source_content": "When used in conjunction with Metadata elements, clicking on any element inside `<Card.Meta>` will prevent the card action to be executed (either `href` to be followed or `onClick` to be called).",
      "source_content_hash": "012da57a59c06c5116459c441a57e4cf76b3caea023126707bdd0caad855a30c",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "メタデータ要素と併用する場合、`<Card.Meta>` 内の要素をクリックすると、カードのアクション（`href` の遷移または `onClick` の呼び出し）が実行されなくなります。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "82e90254",
      "source_content": "Example:",
      "source_content_hash": "872887e563e75957ffc20b021332504f2ddd0a8f3964cb93070863bfaf13cdad",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "例:"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "890e01bc",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card onClick={() => alert('Hello, Grafana!')}>\n  <Card.Heading>Hello, Grafana</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Meta>Clicking on this text (Meta) WILL NOT trigger the alert!</Card.Meta>\n  <Card.Description>Clicking on this text (Description) WILL trigger the alert!</Card.Description>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "a2fc0627ed468445f4af8c712dacdc00957d79479129d6926d65042fe3013ae3",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_890e01bc"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "42a5832e",
      "source_content": "### Inside a list item",
      "source_content_hash": "910dbd24f6b84d835abaf0a75dcf5b16e5d0cd925fa405c9d8cf5cfe745e285e",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### リスト項目内での使用"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "0e80209e",
      "source_content": "To render cards in a list, it is possible to nest them inside `li` items.",
      "source_content_hash": "ab846cd0dfbb43e1c38f8e89372fdff41516ef0a111cc8c566835b2f499f5791",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "カードをリスト内に表示するには、`li` 要素内にネストすることが可能です。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "59534425",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<ul>\n  <li>\n    <Card>\n      <Card.Heading>List card item</Card.Heading>\n      <Card.Description>Card that is rendered inside li element.</Card.Description>\n    </Card>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <Card>\n      <Card.Heading>List card item</Card.Heading>\n      <Card.Description>Card that is rendered inside li element.</Card.Description>\n    </Card>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <Card>\n      <Card.Heading>List card item</Card.Heading>\n      <Card.Description>Card that is rendered inside li element.</Card.Description>\n    </Card>\n  </li>\n  <li>\n    <Card>\n      <Card.Heading>List card item</Card.Heading>\n      <Card.Description>Card that is rendered inside li element.</Card.Description>\n    </Card>\n  </li>\n</ul>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "9a9fca16b41f76123ccf7c488036a3db77db5e628a1350d355d8dce5ecebef21",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_59534425"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "5dba1427",
      "source_content": "### With media elements",
      "source_content_hash": "f89cc154f788bc79d4b09d086876f94f7bd44e9ebc220b801d0c32c114ec7e61",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### メディア要素との併用"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "534ac82e",
      "source_content": "Cards can also be rendered with media content such as icons or images. Such elements need to be wrapped in `Card.Figure` component.",
      "source_content_hash": "e1a9fa25febfb51c648623711518af3323580447139d40ca1f7a34e2fb459e5e",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "カードはアイコンや画像などのメディアコンテンツと一緒に表示することもできます。これらの要素は `Card.Figure` コンポーネントでラップする必要があります。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "01a167f4",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card>\n  <Card.Heading>1-ops-tools1-fallback</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Figure>\n    <img src={logo} alt=\"Grafana Logo\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n  </Card.Figure>\n  <Card.Meta>\n    Grafana\n    <a key=\"prom-link\" href=\"https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\">\n      https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\n    </a>\n  </Card.Meta>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "ad847b880aae68777b28b171390b188081ab0f713bcea661dccc351f87258e18",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_01a167f4"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "c6b2ca77",
      "source_content": "### Action cards",
      "source_content_hash": "2068f5c35ee61648ba2f750fd98723f8f7f86e72cbf840a5a909e5e77a72d3bf",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### アクションカード"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "dce16ab4",
      "source_content": "Cards also accept primary and secondary actions. Usually the primary actions are displayed as buttons while secondary actions are displayed as icon buttons. The actions need to be wrapped in `Card.Actions` and `Card.SecondaryActions` components respectively.",
      "source_content_hash": "f13a70d2b41b89ad729f6135f9f7cadb3eee50d5157e1caaec24ca484070748d",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "カードはプライマリとセカンダリのアクションも受け入れます。通常、プライマリアクションはボタンとして、セカンダリアクションはアイコンボタンとして表示されます。アクションはそれぞれ `Card.Actions` と `Card.SecondaryActions` コンポーネントでラップする必要があります。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "0029045f",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card>\n  <Card.Heading>1-ops-tools1-fallback</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Meta>\n    Grafana\n    <a key=\"prom-link\" href=\"https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\">\n      https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\n    </a>\n  </Card.Meta>\n  <Card.Figure>\n    <img src={logo} alt=\"Grafana Logo\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n  </Card.Figure>\n  <Card.Actions>\n    <Button key=\"settings\" variant=\"secondary\">\n      Settings\n    </Button>\n    <Button key=\"explore\" variant=\"secondary\">\n      Explore\n    </Button>\n  </Card.Actions>\n  <Card.SecondaryActions>\n    <IconButton key=\"showAll\" name=\"apps\" tooltip=\"Show all dashboards for this data source\" />\n    <IconButton key=\"delete\" name=\"trash-alt\" tooltip=\"Delete this data source\" />\n  </Card.SecondaryActions>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "c2a878dd3725fa8f4388e142c8fe82b6f3cce09c9dc784ec23b64b4801f5968f",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_0029045f"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "4b62f7d8",
      "source_content": "### Disabled state",
      "source_content_hash": "bef7605eace0bbd1f0d10405c9ba6b66626e86006a0658f4f3080d75313b17cf",
      "node_type": "heading",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "### 無効状態"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "4899bc54",
      "source_content": "Card can have a disabled state, effectively making it and its actions non-clickable. If there are any actions, they will be disabled instead of the whole card.",
      "source_content_hash": "afbcb175ab396f52ba64fb90d7be688dee7c1fdbc09b743929d5c87d9244adbd",
      "node_type": "paragraph",
      "translatable": true,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "カードを無効状態に設定でき、これによりカードとそのアクションがクリック不可になります。アクションがある場合、カード全体ではなくアクションが無効化されます。"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "21f43a9a",
      "source_content": "```jsx\n<Card disabled>\n  <Card.Heading>1-ops-tools1-fallback</Card.Heading>\n  <Card.Meta>\n    Grafana\n    <a key=\"prom-link\" href=\"https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\">\n      https://ops-us-east4.grafana.net/api/prom\n    </a>\n  </Card.Meta>\n  <Card.Figure>\n    <img src={logo} alt=\"Grafana Logo\" width=\"40\" height=\"40\" />\n  </Card.Figure>\n</Card>\n```",
      "source_content_hash": "9a47c12ff9843cdc9ffc8b1f896655e93e75429aae36d9fa5528279829fa33a2",
      "node_type": "code",
      "translatable": false,
      "translations": {
        "ja": "@@untranslatable_placeholder_21f43a9a"
      }
    },
    {
      "segment_id": "5b2e44c7",
